title: >>> POSTPONEMENT!
body_text:
The votes are still coming in, but it's not hard to realize that DODGEBALL 59 would have been a rough event for various reasons if it were to remain tomorrow, October 6.
With that said, DODGEBALL 59 (and all other events for that matter) will be pushed back one week.
Updated schedule!
DODGEBALL 59 is Saturday, October 14, 2006 (WHS at 6:30pm)
DODGEBALL LX is Saturday, October 21, 2006 (WHS at 6pm)
The percentages from this past week's vote will be posted as soon as possible. I, the writer of dodgeball, do apologize for any inconvenience. Dodgeball will resume Saturday, October 14! Have a great weekend!
